<section id="top" class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-50 via-cyan-50 to-slate-50 py-20 sm:py-24">
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 top-0 -z-10 h-64 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top,#bfdbfe_0%,transparent_70%)]"></div>

  <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-4xl px-4 text-center sm:px-6">
    <div id="start" class="space-y-7">
      <p class="inline-flex rounded-full border border-blue-200 bg-blue-100 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-blue-800">
        Production SaaS Starter
      </p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-black leading-tight tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-5xl">
        따라하면 서비스가 완성되는
        <span class="text-blue-700">웹서비스 구축 패키지</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-lg text-slate-600">
        누구나 단계별로 프로덕션 준비 완료된 SaaS를 직접 구현합니다.
        20개 완전한 문서, GitHub 템플릿 코드, 운영 노하우까지 한 번에 제공합니다.
      </p>
      <p class="mx-auto max-w-2xl rounded-lg border border-blue-100 bg-white/80 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">
        가입 후 10분 안에 첫 SaaS 골격을 실행해볼 수 있습니다.
      </p>

      <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-2xl flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600">
        <span class="rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-3 py-1">평생 접근</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-3 py-1">1년 무료 업데이트</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-3 py-1">7일 이내 100% 환불</span>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center">
        <%= link_to "구매 절차 확인하기", new_user_session_path, class: "inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-blue-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-blue-700" %>
        <%= link_to "커리큘럼 문서 보기", docs_path, class: "inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-blue-200 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-700 transition hover:border-blue-300 hover:bg-blue-50" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
